data.description: AMAZING OPPORTUNITY!!! **PRICE REDUCTION**Buyers will be excited to see this charming two story 4 bdrm, 2.5 bath, 2 car gem with 3 living areas in desirable neighborhood of Bulverde Creek. Corner fireplace, Wood Grain Luxury Vinyl Tile throughout (carpeted stairs/closets). The large master bedroom offers two walk-in closets and spacious bath. Bonus room upstairs is surrounded by the bedrooms and can bring many options for extra space. All schools are near with easy access. Open floorplan, NEST Smart Thermostat, Newer Oven/Cooktop, Outside A/C (2022), Water Heater (2021). Covered patio great for entertaining. (Large planter stays). Top rated NEISD school district and Johnson high school! Easy access to 1604 and 281 with lots of shopping and restaurants nearby! Move in and make memories!
